name: Leica M2 Pier #02 Sätila, Sweden
description:
The Leica M2 Collection, part of an ongoing series.
I took this photo with the wonderful Leica M2 camera, which was introduced in the late 1950s. It is usually the legendary Super Angulon 21mm f4 lens and black and white film that I use. With this setup, I generally shoot landscapes and cityscapes in a contemplative style. A JPEG derived from a negative result using a digital camera.
